### Login empleado
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login/employee
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "employeeId": "130053"
}

### Login admin
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login/admin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "lomartin",
  "password": "12,Briefing?"
}

### Obtener briefing publico
GET http://localhost:3001/api/public/briefing
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_SESSION_TOKEN

### Crear briefing
POST http://localhost:3001/api/admin/briefings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Briefing Operaciones",
  "edition": "2026-W15",
  "briefingAt": "2026-04-10T10:00:00.000Z",
  "votingEndsAt": "2026-04-09T18:00:00.000Z",
  "status": "open"
}

### Crear tema anonimo
POST http://localhost:3001/api/public/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_SESSION_TOKEN

{
  "briefingId": "REPLACE_BRIEFING_ID",
  "title": "Dependencias con legal",
  "description": "Aclarar impacto de validaciones legales en los plazos."
}

### Votar tema
POST http://localhost:3001/api/public/votes
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_SESSION_TOKEN

{
  "briefingId": "REPLACE_BRIEFING_ID",
  "topicId": "REPLACE_TOPIC_ID"
}

### Cambiar estado de un tema
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/admin/topics/REPLACE_TOPIC_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_ADMIN_SESSION_TOKEN

{
  "status": "treated"
}

### Listar empleados
GET http://localhost:3001/api/admin/employees
Authorization: Bearer REPLACE_ADMIN_SESSION_TOKEN
